<br>
I like the new changes.  It makes the guild warriors think twice before telling me not to stun.  When you get clipped by big dots and big dds, you think twice about telling your only stunner that can really take the hits to back off, and that makes my job easier.  When it was small stuff, it was always &quot;Dal, don't pull aggro.&quot;  &quot;Dal, how do you have aggro?&quot;  &quot;Dal, blast you, ease up on those stuns!&quot;  I admit that I overstun at times..  But I'll live with the mitigated damage ;p  I have no problems with being paranoid about castings.. <p><a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=60479>Dalantia Dragonet</a><br>
